%h1
  LETS PREDICT
  %span{:style => 'font-size:16px;'} Fantasy Leagues, Simplified.

= form_tag sessions_path, :method => :post, :class => 'well', :style => 'width:350px;' do
  %legend Login
  .controls
    = text_field_tag "user[login]", "", :placeholder => 'LDAP Username', :class => 'input-large'
  .controls
    = password_field_tag "user[password]", "", :placeholder => 'LDAP Password', :class => 'input-large'
  .actions
    = submit_tag "Go", :class => 'btn btn-success'

%h3 How does it work!
.pull-left{:style => 'width:550px;'}
  %ul
    %li Login to view the list of active tournaments, that starts in a month.
    %li
      Click 'Predict Now' and start predicting the winning teams for the listed matches.
    %li
      You can choose to predict only few matches at once, then click 'Submit' to save your predictions.
      %br
      May sure to come back again and complete your predictions.
    %li 
      %b Predictions for a tournament closes a day before the start of the tournament.

.pull-left{:style => 'width:550px;'}
  %ul
    %li
      Each <b>correct prediction is awarded with points</b> based on the match type:
      %ul
        %li League - 2 points
        %li Semifinal/Eliminator/Qualifier - 4 points
        %li Final - 8 points
    %li No negative points for wrong predictions.
    %li
      Points for the completed matches will be updated on the next working day.
      %br
      You can use 'View Results' to see the results of your predictions.
      %br
      Also you can use 'Check Leaderboard' to see your position among other users.
      %br
      Clicking on the name of the user will display the results of his/her predictions.
    %li
      %b Top three winners will get an awesome prize.

%div{:style => 'clear:left;'}
